00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:20,200
Right, eighth.

586
00:35:21,040 --> 00:35:23,200
If someone asks us who looks better,

587
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,280
what do you say?

588
00:35:26,760 --> 00:35:29,480
I can only choose between you two.

589
00:35:29,720 --> 00:35:31,040
Not you.

590
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,000
Remember.

591
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:33,600
You have to tell anyone.

592
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:35,280
My sister is the prettiest.

593
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:36,880
I'm the second one.

594
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,760
Got it.

595
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,400
I have another question.

596
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:46,040
If someone asks you who is the best swordsman in Qinglong Fortress,

597
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:46,920
what would you say?

598
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:47,840
I know.

599
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:49,120
You're the first and she's the second.

600
00:35:49,360 --> 00:35:50,440
No, she won't.

601
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:51,440
I'm second.

602
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:54,040
If you're second, who dares to be the first?

603
00:35:54,520 --> 00:35:55,560
My father.

604
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:57,120
Yes, Madam.

605
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:00,120
Madam.

606
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,120
Madam.

607
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,960
Did he remove all his weapons?

608
00:36:06,680 --> 00:36:07,680
They're all here.

609
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,800
Show me.

610
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,280
Madam, this way.

611
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:20,360
Eagle.

612
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,480
Sir. Father.

613
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,400
Uncle.

614
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:33,960
Take them back to their room.

615
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,400
Miss Leng.

616
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:01,000
Are you Shangguan Bao?

617
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,560
Bastard!

618
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,360
How dare you talk to Madam?

619
00:37:04,680 --> 00:37:05,720
What’s your name?

620
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:06,960
Wu Zhen.

621
00:37:07,720 --> 00:37:09,160
Do you want to be a swordsman?

622
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:13,000
I can follow you.

623
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:14,880
What did you say?

624
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:16,400
I mean

625
00:37:16,800 --> 00:37:18,640
I’ll follow your order.

626
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:21,280
What if I want you to die?

627
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:32,240
It depends on your fate tomorrow.

628
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,240
Shangguan Bao

629
00:37:48,360 --> 00:37:50,520
is not a simple leader of swordsmen.

630
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,320
I can only stay here

631
00:37:53,640 --> 00:37:55,320
to find out what happened.

632
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:05,120
Why are there so many Japanese in Shanzhou?

633
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:17,600
Brigade Commander, what are you thinking?

634
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:21,960
I'm thinking

635
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:25,960
why the Japanese arrived in Shaanxi so soon.

636
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,640
How did you know

637
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:29,640
those people were not swordsmen yesterday?

638
00:38:29,640 --> 00:38:30,720
but Japanese.

639
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:34,560
At this time,

640
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:37,880
It can't be the Communist Party.

641
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:41,480
The swordsmen wouldn't have covered their faces.

642
00:38:41,480 --> 00:38:43,960
And their weapons are very delicate.

643
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:46,680
Only the Japanese.

644
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:50,560
I remember.

645
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,600
Looks like the Japanese really came here.

646
00:39:03,240 --> 00:39:04,880
Search! Search!

647
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,440
Search one by one.

648
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:11,360
Which part are you from?

649
00:39:11,800 --> 00:39:13,080
Which part are you in?

650
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,280
Which part?

651
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:16,320
Which part? Are you blind?

652
00:39:16,640 --> 00:39:17,560
Drop the gun. Drop the gun.

653
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:19,120
Okay, okay.

654
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,880
What are you doing?

655
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:25,440
Sir, we're here to collect money.

656
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,320
What money?

657
00:39:28,520 --> 00:39:31,480
Sir, there are too many bandits here.

658
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,320
They took money from bandits.

659
00:39:34,280 --> 00:39:35,320
Why did those bandits

660
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:36,640
still act recklessly?

661
00:39:36,960 --> 00:39:37,960
This...

662
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:40,680
Because there are too many bandits,

663
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,480
we can't defeat them.

664
00:39:42,720 --> 00:39:44,000
Where is your captain?

665
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,640
The captain went to buy a birthday gift.

666
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,320
Who's celebrating his birthday?

667
00:39:48,640 --> 00:39:50,200
It's Shangguan Bao's birthday. It's his 60th birthday.

668
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,600
Our captain

669
00:39:54,600 --> 00:39:55,600
Shangguan Bao.

670
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,120
Yes.

671
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,880
Leader of Qinglong Camp, Shangguan Bao.

672
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:01,440
Yes.

673
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:07,200
Get lost.

674
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:08,720
Yes.

675
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:09,800
Let's go.

676
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:23,520
You two go get ready.

677
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:25,280
Let's go up the mountain.

678
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:27,680
