679
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:28,800
Yes.

680
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:32,200
Hurry up.

681
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:33,840
Come on. Come on.

682
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:37,800
Stand still.

683
00:40:40,240 --> 00:40:41,160
Wu Zhen.

684
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:43,960
My daughter wants you to be her bodyguard.

685
00:40:44,240 --> 00:40:45,960
You have to show her your skills.

686
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,360
Brother.

687
00:40:55,720 --> 00:40:57,640
I used to be your bodyguard.

688
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:59,120
Since you're here,

689
00:40:59,360 --> 00:41:01,200
