690
00:41:12,560 --> 00:41:13,440
Please.

691
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:20,560
Is he okay?

692
00:41:21,120 --> 00:41:21,840
Our boss

693
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:23,920
