694
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:25,800
Even the old man praised his cutting skills.

695
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:28,040
I don't think he can beat him.

696
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,920
What do you know? Go.

697
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:31,560
We'll see.

698
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:13,720
It doesn't look good.

699
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:15,800
I just think he's quite interesting.

700
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:17,280
